efault `variant` is wrong. Upstream `BadgeVariant` defaults to `\"solid\"`, not `\"weak\"`, so omitting `variant` renders a filled badge rather than the weak style described here."},{"severity":"MEDIUM","file":"plugins/daangn-seed-ai/skills/seed/references/components/badge.md","line":105,"message":"The truncation widths are swapped. Upstream rootage/CSS use `medium` at about `7.5rem` max width and `large` at about `6.75rem`, but this table documents the opposite values."}]}
